title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 2X GTA$ and 4X RP on Simeon Contact Missions
content:
Earn some extra GTA$ and rank up quickly this week with 2X GTA$ and 4X RP on all Simeon Contact Missions, including Premium Deluxe Repo Work.

TIP: Call Simeon to get started on a random mission or use the Online section of the Pause Menu to join a Job of your choice from the Rockstar Created Missions list.
